00:36:07.520 --> 00:36:11.710 align:middle line:84%
all of it, is simply a distorted
version of the ancient moon

00:36:11.710 --> 00:36:13.080 align:middle line:90%
religion.

00:36:13.080 --> 00:36:14.330 align:middle line:90%
Crucified on the cross.

00:36:14.330 --> 00:36:15.910 align:middle line:84%
The cross is the
symbol for the moon

00:36:15.910 --> 00:36:18.610 align:middle line:84%
in all pre-Christian
cultures worldwide.

00:36:18.610 --> 00:36:21.690 align:middle line:84%
He's crucified on a Friday,
which is Friars Day.

00:36:21.690 --> 00:36:23.240 align:middle line:90%
She's the moon goddess.

00:36:23.240 --> 00:36:26.663 align:middle line:84%
He's resurrected on Monday,
which is my Moon Day.

00:36:26.663 --> 00:36:30.370 align:middle line:84%
And he's resurrected three
days later, then he dies.

00:36:30.370 --> 00:36:34.400 align:middle line:84%
Now three is important for
several reasons in the moon

00:36:34.400 --> 00:36:35.280 align:middle line:90%
culture.

00:36:35.280 --> 00:36:40.040 align:middle line:84%
One, the moon has three
colors, white, red, and black.

00:36:40.040 --> 00:36:42.534 align:middle line:90%
So the moon has three colors.

00:36:42.534 --> 00:36:44.170 align:middle line:84%
And what's more
important than that?

00:36:44.170 --> 00:36:44.970 align:middle line:90%
Oh, yeah.

00:36:44.970 --> 00:36:48.090 align:middle line:84%
The other thing, of course,
is that earth, moon, and sun

00:36:48.090 --> 00:36:52.200 align:middle line:84%
are considered to be
mother, father, child.

00:36:52.200 --> 00:36:57.270 align:middle line:84%
And the earth is the child,
the daughter of the sun

00:36:57.270 --> 00:36:58.420 align:middle line:90%
and the moon.

00:36:58.420 --> 00:37:00.440 align:middle line:84%
That was part of
the moon religion.

00:37:00.440 --> 00:37:03.750 align:middle line:84%
So the three is important
for several reasons.

00:37:03.750 --> 00:37:08.560 align:middle line:84%
Christ is said to be born
of the 25th of December.

00:37:08.560 --> 00:37:11.040 align:middle line:84%
Now that's three
days-- did you say

00:37:11.040 --> 00:37:14.770 align:middle line:84%
three-- three days after the
shortest day when the sun is

00:37:14.770 --> 00:37:18.160 align:middle line:84%
reborn every year after
the moon sacrifices him

00:37:18.160 --> 00:37:19.430 align:middle line:90%
on the shortest day.

00:37:19.430 --> 00:37:21.960 align:middle line:84%
She sacrifices him,
and then resurrects him

00:37:21.960 --> 00:37:23.250 align:middle line:90%
so that life can continue.

00:37:23.250 --> 00:37:26.010 align:middle line:90%


00:37:26.010 --> 00:37:28.210 align:middle line:84%
>>Could the story
of Jesus Christ

00:37:28.210 --> 00:37:34.526 align:middle line:84%
