story of Neanderthal rituals?

00:37:34.526 --> 00:37:37.224 align:middle line:84%
Could our most cherished
religious beliefs

00:37:37.224 --> 00:37:41.750 align:middle line:84%
originate with the Neanderthals,
such as the concepts

00:37:41.750 --> 00:37:45.144 align:middle line:84%
