for living, but they

00:41:11.700 --> 00:41:13.175 align:middle line:90%
used it to perform rituals.

00:41:13.175 --> 00:41:18.420 align:middle line:90%


00:41:18.420 --> 00:41:22.360 align:middle line:10%
Daniel Ruzo considered
that everywhere else

00:41:22.360 --> 00:41:25.540 align:middle line:10%
in the world, the legends
and the sculptures

00:41:25.540 --> 00:41:27.580 align:middle line:10%
