00:48:04.700 --> 00:48:06.210 align:middle line:10%
And we're here in the evening.

00:48:06.210 --> 00:48:07.530 align:middle line:10%
The sun is setting.

00:48:07.530 --> 00:48:10.060 align:middle line:10%
