00:48:10.060 --> 00:48:11.640 align:middle line:10%
>>Direct line to the eye.

00:48:11.640 --> 00:48:13.340 align:middle line:10%
>>Direct line to the eye.

00:48:13.340 --> 00:48:17.850 align:middle line:10%
This Neanderthal-type face
is looking toward the west,

00:48:17.850 --> 00:48:20.100 align:middle line:10%
looking toward the setting sun.

00:48:20.100 --> 00:48:23.250 align:middle line:10%
Now it's been speculated
that Neanderthals

00:48:23.250 --> 00:48:25.730 align:middle line:10%
were a more nocturnal species.

00:48:25.730 --> 00:48:29.700 align:middle line:10%
