00:48:29.700 --> 00:48:30.810 align:middle line:10%
The setting sun.

00:48:30.810 --> 00:48:33.860 align:middle line:10%
The sun that sets
as they come out

00:48:33.860 --> 00:48:37.550 align:middle line:10%
for their nocturnal
activities, their ceremonies,

00:48:37.550 --> 00:48:38.670 align:middle line:10%
their rituals.

00:48:38.670 --> 00:48:40.900 align:middle line:10%
So they would not be
looking toward the east

00:48:40.900 --> 00:48:45.670 align:middle line:10%
as many modern cultures
do, but toward the west.

00:48:45.670 --> 00:48:48.840 align:middle line:10%
The setting sun, which would
be significant and important

00:48:48.840 --> 00:48:52.200 align:middle line:10%
to them, because essentially,
that would start their day.

00:48:52.200 --> 00:48:54.710 align:middle line:10%
That would start
their ceremonies.

00:48:54.710 --> 00:48:58.520 align:middle line:10%
And here we have a
Neanderthal-like face

00:48:58.520 --> 00:49:00.780 align:middle line:10%
looking toward the setting sun.

00:49:00.780 --> 00:49:07.650 align:middle line:84%
