00:50:30.310 --> 00:50:31.490 align:middle line:90%
There could have been.

00:50:31.490 --> 00:50:33.480 align:middle line:90%
I can't say for certain.

00:50:33.480 --> 00:50:38.570 align:middle line:84%
But I think more importantly
