00:57:39.950 --> 00:57:44.790 align:middle line:84%
Another feature that is on the
plateau that really struck me

00:57:44.790 --> 00:57:50.880 align:middle line:84%
is what we can call the bearded
head or the bearded man's head.

00:57:50.880 --> 00:57:53.350 align:middle line:90%
It's a huge structure.

00:57:53.350 --> 00:57:56.280 align:middle line:84%
Very powerful, very
moving in my mind.

00:57:56.280 --> 00:58:00.390 align:middle line:84%
And I suspect that whether
