may have survived

00:58:06.800 --> 00:58:11.680 align:middle line:84%
from a very long time
ago, geologically,

00:58:11.680 --> 00:58:14.950 align:middle line:84%
and may have moved people
and been recognized

00:58:14.950 --> 00:58:19.120 align:middle line:84%
by people, specifically
Neanderthals,

00:58:19.120 --> 00:58:20.840 align:middle line:84%
before the end of
the last ice age.

00:58:20.840 --> 00:58:24.490 align:middle line:84%
That they would have recognized
this as looking like a face,

00:58:24.490 --> 00:58:28.700 align:middle line:84%
