would form a perfect stage

00:59:44.060 --> 00:59:47.370 align:middle line:10%
for ceremonies, for
ritual practices,

00:59:47.370 --> 00:59:49.980 align:middle line:10%
for initiation,
for other types of

00:59:49.980 --> 00:59:53.030 align:middle line:10%
sacred and religious practices.

00:59:53.030 --> 00:59:56.470 align:middle line:84%
