01:00:15.970 --> 01:00:18.750 align:middle line:84%
So I think this could be
a very powerful setting

01:00:18.750 --> 01:00:21.380 align:middle line:90%
for ceremonial purposes.

01:00:21.380 --> 01:00:25.020 align:middle line:84%
All of the pieces, in
